🚀 PromptVault — Breakdown & Upgrade Plan
💡 Core Idea (Already Strong)

Tumne jo define kiya hai wo bilkul market-fit hai:

Prompt = asset
Log usko lose kar dete hain
Tum = organize + reuse + share layer

Ye same problem har AI user face karta hai 👇
👉 creators, devs, marketers, freelancers — sab

🧠 Isko aur powerful kaise bana sakte ho
1. 🔍 Smart AI Tagging (Gemini ka killer use)

Sirf auto-tagging mat karo — isko intelligent banao:

Prompt intent detect karo (e.g. “copywriting”, “coding”, “SEO”)
Difficulty level assign karo (Beginner / Pro)
Output type classify karo (blog, code, tweet)

👉 Ye tumhe normal vault se AI-powered vault bana dega

2. 🧩 Prompt Templates (Game Changer Feature)

Raw prompts se zyada powerful hota hai:

"Write a LinkedIn post about {{topic}} in {{tone}} tone"
Users variables fill kare → reusable system
Isko bolo: Dynamic Prompts
3. 🌍 Community Vault (🔥 viral feature)

Tumne already mention kiya — good move

Isme add karo:

Upvote / save system
“Trending prompts”
Creator profiles

👉 Ye tumhe bana dega:
“GitHub for Prompts”

4. 🧾 Export System (Already good, but upgrade)

Tumne diya:

JSON ✅
Notion ✅
PDF ✅

Add karo:

Copy as Markdown
Direct share link (public page)
5. 🔐 Personal vs Public Vault UX

Clear separation hona chahiye:

Private prompts (default)
Public prompts (shareable)

👉 Toggle simple rakho:
[Private 🔒] [Public 🌍]

🏗️ Suggested Architecture (MERN)
📦 Backend (Node + Express)
Auth (JWT)
Prompt CRUD
Tagging API (Gemini integration)
Community feed
🗄️ DB (MongoDB)

Collections:

users
prompts
tags
likes / saves
🎨 Frontend (React)

Pages:

Dashboard (your vault)
Explore (community)
Prompt Editor
Profile
⚡ MVP Plan (agar jaldi launch karna hai)

Phase 1:

Auth
Create / Save prompt
Manual tags
Personal vault

Phase 2:

AI tagging (Gemini)
Community vault
Upvotes

Phase 3:

Templates
Export system
Public profiles
💰 Future Monetization (optional but smart)
Freemium:
Free → limited prompts
Pro → unlimited + AI tagging
Premium prompt marketplace 👀
🧠 Honest Feedback

👉 Idea weak nahi hai — execution pe game hai
👉 Agar tumne:

UX clean rakha
AI tagging smooth banaya
Community active ki

Toh ye actual startup ban sakta hai

